_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     this function access the transformation matrix attached to a
     "BrainSpace" object

_U_s_a_g_e:

     trans(x)

_A_r_g_u_m_e_n_t_s:

       x: an object derived from "BrainData" or "BrainSpace" classes 

_D_e_t_a_i_l_s:

     transformation matrices are 4X4 affine matrices for 3D images and
     3X3 matrices for 2D images

_V_a_l_u_e:

     the transformation matrix

